[
  "Matt Moulding founded Manchester based e-commerce company The Hut Group in 2004 and took it public as THG Holdings in September 2020.",
  "The Hut Group runs over 100 websites selling everything from fashion to nutrition and beauty across 164 countries.",
  "Moulding got his start working alongside fellow billionaire John Caudwell at U.K. retailer Phones4U.",
  "The Hut Group develops and sells its proprietary technology to the likes of Nintendo and Walgreens.",
  "Moulding owns about 25% of The Hut Group, which listed on the London Stock Exchange in September 2020."
]